## Remarks  
<span data-ttu-id="18a75-276">Метод `Close` освобождает как неуправляемые, так и управляемые ресурсы, связанные с <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18a75-276">The `Close` method frees both unmanaged and managed resources associated with the <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="18a75-277">Если <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream> владеет базовым <xref:System.Net.Sockets.Socket>, он также закрывается.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18a75-277">If the <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream> owns the underlying <xref:System.Net.Sockets.Socket>, it is closed as well.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="18a75-278">Если <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream> был связан с <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>, метод `Close` закроет TCP-соединение, но не удалит связанный <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18a75-278">If a <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream> was associated with a <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>, the `Close` method will close the TCP connection, but not dispose of the associated <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>.</span></span>

## Examples  
<span data-ttu-id="18a75-279">В следующем примере кода закрывается <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18a75-279">The following code example closes the <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>.</span></span>

```vb
' Example for closing the NetworkStream.
' Close the NetworkStream
myNetworkStream.Close()
```

```csharp
// Example for closing the NetworkStream.

// Close the NetworkStream
myNetworkStream.Close();
```

```cpp
// Example for closing the NetworkStream.
// Close the NetworkStream
myNetworkStream->Close();
```
